data.description: PRICE REDUCED!!! Enjoy this remarkable 3 bed 2 bath home in desirably growing area of Mission, Tx at an amazing price.  This lovely home boasts a bonus room that can accommodate one's desires like gaming, crafting, storage, etc.  The back yard completes the home with a covered patio set amongst mature trees and covered car port with a shed.  The listed square footage includes an air conditioned bonus room, making this home comfortably spacious!  Enjoy the comfort of having a one year old roof!  Don't miss out on this opportunity on one of the best priced homes in this area!
